OBI Study Design: C evidence and (is_specified_output_of some ('study design execution' and (realizes some (concretizes some %))))
OBI Independent Variable: C evidence and (is_specified_output_of some ('study design execution' and (realizes some (concretizes some ('study design' and 'has part' some 'study design independent variable' and 'is about' some %)))))
OBI Dependent Variable: C evidence and (is_specified_output_of some ('study design execution' and (realizes some (concretizes some ('study design' and 'has part' some 'study design dependent variable' and 'is about' some %)))))

Comment: OBI mappings should come from OBI or GO - enter in the term labels in their respective column. All of these will appear as 'equivalent'.
